---
title: Date picker
---
p.-text
  | Date pickers are used for inputting dates from the user. It might be toggled when the user focuses
  | an input of type date in a form.

h3 Examples
p.-text
  | Here is an example of a date picker not attached to any element.

- var day = 1;
- var weekS = ['Sun', 'Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat'];
- var weekS = ['S', 'M', 'T', 'W', 'T', 'F', 'S'];
- var today = 19;
- var active = 23;

h4 Base
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .m-datepicker.-weekStartsOnSun.-monthStartsOnThu
      .m-datepicker__monthRow
        .prev.-disabled
          i.a-icon.icon-chevron-left.-sm
        .m-datepicker__month
          | November 2018
        .next
          i.a-icon.icon-chevron-right.-sm.-text--brand
      .m-datepicker__dayNames
        each weekDay in weekS
          .m-datepicker__weekDay=weekDay
      .m-datepicker__days
        while day < 31
          if day === today
            .m-datepicker__day.-today=day++
          else if day === active
            .m-datepicker__day.-active=day++
          else if day < today
            .m-datepicker__day.-inactive=day++
          else
            .m-datepicker__day=day++


